<p>As has become tradition, once per year Macworld Expo&#8217;s Paul Kent comes on the Mac Geek Gab to give us his info, perspective and most importantly his vision of the show this year. Tune in and spend some time with Paul as he tells us what they&#8217;ve cooked up and what he sees as the important aspects of this year&#8217;s annual Mac market gathering!</p>
